{"tid":39374,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"「笑一笑世界更美妙」跑車篇","createTime":"2016-12-14T14:06:44.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-15T10:14:15.000Z","uid":17896,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f15e4667b30e9f3853b43d6e37dce812c04393e8","tid":39374,"uid":17896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:06:44.000Z","msg":"昨日我菲律賓既工人同我講，樓下電器鋪請左個後生仔叫小明，又高又靚仔，聽講仲幾有家底。有一天小明遲到，電器老闆就氣沖沖打比小明「小明你去到邊呀？」，小明氣定神閒回覆「唔好意思呀老闆，我揸緊車返黎，有小小塞車，好快好快」<br />\n<br />\n十分鐘過去...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n三十分鐘過去...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n電器老闆突然見到門口停左架黃色既跑車係門口，見到小明落車，老闆就串小明「嘩架跑車好靚喎，可惜呀唔夠快，返黎都要成一個鐘」<br />\n<br />\n小明得意道「我嫁跑車時速去到幾多幾多公里，買左幾多幾多錢嫁」<br />\n<br />\n老闆「如果印三個紅色字係車身，包你下次返工實準時！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/14/220525_3f76d46c4f29c27da965a9b6b0631f5d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F14%2F220525_3f76d46c4f29c27da965a9b6b0631f5d.jpg&h=aa014862&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0ccf83f669147ab52ab0ee36264eea5b21840f08","tid":39374,"uid":17896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:11:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e76a979bbf843b43b7b69df7e0c18231e2c8cf4","tid":39374,"uid":17896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T15:48:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cb5493b7a8d0a202fcce0167c99cf892a2f8ec9","tid":39374,"uid":17896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T10:14:15.000Z","msg":"推"}]}